relevant_findings.heent: Sclera icteric, pupils equal, round, reactive to light, extraocular movements intact, oral cavity clear, mucous membranes moist
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezing, rales, or rhonchi
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, non-tender, non-distended, positive bowel sounds
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented times three, cranial nerves II-XII grossly intact, moving all extremities well
